      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me with a depreciation problem for my accounting class? i need to find the annual depreciation for a machine that cost 50000 but has a salvage value of 5000 and a useful life of 5 years. can u show the formula and how u get the answer?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
